OL,7,FThe acquittal was finalised when the
OL,8,Fprosecution waved its right to appeal,
OL,9,Fending Hakamada's near 60-year legal
OL,10,Fbattle to prove his innocence.
OL,12,FShizuoka Prefectural Police Chief
OL,13,FTakayoshi Tsuda visited the 88-year-
OL,14,Fold Hakamada at his home and offered
OL,15,Fan apology in person.
