OL,3,CJapanese man receives apology after
OL,4,Cwrongly spending over 50 years on
OL,5,Cdeath row
OL,7,F"We are sorry to have caused you
OL,8,Funspeakable mental distress and burden
OL,9,Ffor as long as 58 years from the time
OL,10,Fof the arrest until the acquittal was
OL,11,Ffinalised," Tsuda said, as he stood in
OL,12,Ffront of Hakamada and then bowed
OL,13,Fdeeply.
OL,15,F"We are terribly sorry," Tsuda added,
OL,16,Fpromising a "meticulous and
OL,17,Fappropriate investigation."
