OL,7,FHakamada, who has difficulty carrying
OL,8,Fout conversation due to his mental
OL,9,Fcondition from the decades of death
OL,10,Frow confinement, responded: "What it
OL,11,Fmeans to have the authority ... Once
OL,12,Fyou have the power, you're not
OL,13,Fsupposed to grumble."
OL,15,FHakamada's 91-year-old sister, who had
OL,16,Fstood by her brother and now lives
OL,17,Fwith him, thanked the police chief for
OL,18,Fvisiting them.
