OL,7,FHakamada was arrested in August 1966,
OL,8,Fin the killing of an executive at a
OL,9,Fmiso bean paste company and three of
OL,10,Fhis family members in Hamamatsu,
OL,11,Fcentral Japan.
OL,13,FHe was initially sentenced to death in
OL,14,Fa 1968 district court ruling but was
OL,15,Fnot executed because of the lengthy
OL,16,Fappeal and retrial process in Japan.
