OL,7,FIt took nearly three decades for the
OL,8,FSupreme Court to deny his first appeal
OL,9,Ffor a re-trial. His second appeal for
OL,10,Fa re-trial, filed by his sister in
OL,11,F2008, was granted in 2014. The court
OL,12,Fordered his release from his death row
OL,13,Fsolitary cell but without removing his
OL,14,Fconviction, pending the retrial
OL,15,Fprocess.
